   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"20th year, Pauni 19. Give from the account of Julius Theon and Julius Theon to Harpaesis, potter for the lower estate, for wages for the manufacture of wine-carrying jars which he is manufacturing in the pottery of the lower estate . . . through Kallineikes: forty drachmas.;(2nd hd.) Give the 40 drachmas."</ab>
